data.description: Welcome to 748 Talmalge Hall.  This beautiful, and spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, and 2 car detached garage home sits nestled amongst mature trees, on a corner lot in the golf course community of River Plantation.  With an open floor plan, there is plenty of room for family to relax, or entertain guests.  The living room, open to the dining, kitchen, wet bar, and breakfast room provides a natural flow throughout the home.  Huge shower in the primary bathroom, and 2 walk in closets!  Relax in the open, and spacious back yard under the covered patio that provides evening shade. Conroe ISD schools.  Property has a whole house water filter / softener, and a hot water recirculator! No flooding, and fridge stay with the home!  Be sure to check out the virtual tour of the property! Schedule your showing, and come see why this home is perfect for your, and your family!
